name: Reborn
description: Montage created in 25 December 2015 as illustration for a writer's short story. Made with pieces from several photos taken around São Paulo city, including Araçá cemetery and the monument at Pátio do Colégio (see HeN OBJKT 209596). Originally released as HeN OBJKT 21991 on 3 April 2021. Colors tweaked for NFT re-release.
